data.description: Discover a unique opportunity in Ocean Shores! This residence boasts 2058 sqft of living space situated on 120 ft of waterfront across a double lot with a dock and boat launch. It features a 2 car-garage, a wood stove, and a circular driveway providing ample parking. Enjoy the convenience of launching your boat or fishing in your own backyard. The seller is offering to sell this remarkable home fully furnished at no extra cost,  allowing you to immediately start enjoying it. The home is part of the optional community Club and is both open and well-built, making it an opportunity you won't want to miss!
